No any interfaces was changed

Changes was maked for next cases:

- Not a primitive links or types
- No side effects
- File not a test
- If memory allocation and returns exist
- If return exist
- If complex operation
- If increase readability
- Single place of usage - no need on other conditional cases
- If paint method
- If synchronized method body inside init
- If xml processing

